Expanding $(n - 1)^4$ gives $n^4 - 4n^3 + 6n^2 - 4n + 1$. So we need $n^4 - 4n^3 + 6n^2 - 4n + 1 > 2n$, or $n^4 - 4n^3 + 6n^2 - 6n + 1 > 0$.

